{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cc84058f58","title":"对外交部关于美议员访华团成员问题请示报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"158bb11500","index":0,"year":1974,"month":8,"day":27,"articleId":"cc84058f58"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"419944525a","type":"title","text":"对外交部关于美议员访华团成员问题请示报告\"的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"cc84058f58"},{"id":"aa8ad414d1","type":"paragraph","text":"都可以来，多做工作，表示欢迎","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"cc84058f58"},{"id":"4b7e80c72c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"cc84058f58"},{"id":"28d09cff1b","type":"paragraph","text":"八月廿七日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"cc84058f58"},{"id":"262d6210b2","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]国务院副总理邓小平1974年8月26日报送的这个外交部请示报告中说，美议员团定于9月2日至14日访问我国。美方原在8月14日通知我方说，该团由众议院共和党领袖罗兹任团长。8月22日又通知我方，团长改由民主党参议员、参议院外交委员会主席富布赖特担任，团员有参议员2人众议员4人。经查，在4名众议员中有2人是众议院的亲蒋派，他们于今年2月和4月两次访台，发表亲蒋言论。我们考虑，对美方有意塞进两个亲蒋派应做出必要的反应，以使美方今后有所收敛。据此我们草拟了给我驻美联络处的电报稿，请一并审核。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"cc84058f58"}],"page":{"id":"2fbe07e4f9","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"cc84058f58","start":505,"end":505}}}},"__N_SSG":true}